  nf-options greeks NIFTY --expiry 17FEB --strikes 25000 25500  Option greeks
  nf-options expiries NIFTY                       Show upcoming expiries
  nf-options buy NIFTY 17FEB26 25500 PE 1 --dry-run  Preview order

Examples (Stock Options — any F&O-eligible stock):
  nf-options chain RELIANCE                       Show RELIANCE option chain
