  nf-options buy RELIANCE 30MAR26 1400 CE 1 --dry-run  Preview stock option order
  nf-options plan RELIANCE --expiry 2026-03-30 --bias bullish --capital 50000
  nf-options fno-symbols                          List all F&O-eligible stock symbols

Spreads / Strategy Builder (multi-leg basket orders):
  nf-options spread SHREECEM --expiry 2026-04-28 --legs BUY:24250:CE SELL:25000:CE --dry-run
  nf-options spread NIFTY --expiry 2026-04-03 --legs BUY:23000:CE SELL:23500:CE --lots 1
  nf-options spread NIFTY --expiry 2026-04-03 --legs SELL:23200:PE BUY:23000:PE --lots 1  (Bull Put)
  nf-options spread NIFTY --expiry 2026-04-03 --legs BUY:23000:CE BUY:23000:PE --lots 1  (Straddle)
  nf-options spread NIFTY --expiry 2026-04-03 --legs SELL:23200:CE BUY:23400:CE SELL:22800:PE BUY:22600:PE  (Iron Condor)

Common:
  nf-options charges BANKNIFTY 2026-03-12 48000 CE 1 --side BUY     Charges estimate
  nf-options positions                            Show all F&O positions
""",
    )

    sub = parser.add_subparsers(dest="command", help="Command")

    _sym_help = "Symbol (NIFTY, BANKNIFTY, or any F&O stock e.g. RELIANCE, TCS, HDFCBANK)"

    # chain
    p_chain = sub.add_parser("chain", help="Show option chain (index or stock)")
